{"title":"瀚海行舟","authors":["刘连勇","赵亚洲"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瀚海行舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵亚洲　摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘连勇　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道没人告诉你们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前方布满了困难？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被云吸榨得像麻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被风煎炒得滚烫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道没有感到脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步步紧逼的气浪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周汹涌黄色波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞失了天地迷茫了方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么驼队依然前行？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么驼铃依然叮当？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硕大的蹄印坚实的脚印，踏下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一丝摇晃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么像船剪开沙海？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么像剑刺破蛮荒？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏要在黄褐色的意象里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创作一组葱绿的诗行！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}